title: Beautiful Venice in 1900 in color! [A.I enhanced & colorized]

sources.title: Beautiful Venice in 1900 in color! [A.I enhanced & colorized]
sources.description: Take a trip in our time machine to Venice to see how beautiful this city was more than 120 years ago. The film shows most of the famous tourist spots like The Grand Canal, The Bridge of Sighs, The Doge's Palace, San Marco Square, Beautiful canals and bridges, The Rialto bridge, Gondola's and much more. Some footage is even earlier (1898). This is A.I. restored and colorized B&W footage. Music: Haempus Naesselius an other.
